body_html: @dhananjaisharma10 The warning messages tell you that the binaries that were used to install TensorFlow were not optimized for your system architecture. This is almost for every case where we use pre-built binaries for installation. However they can be optimized if you install TensorFlow from source. This will eradicate those warning messages.

body: @dhananjaisharma10 The warning messages tell you that the binaries that were used to install TensorFlow were not optimized for your system architecture. This is almost for every case where we use pre-built binaries for installation. However they can be optimized if you [install TensorFlow from source](https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_sources). This will eradicate those warning messages.
